text: "\n <div id=\"moduleIndex\">\n  # Jack-in-the-Box\n  1. Create a user interface\
  \ (GUI) that has a single button labeled \"Surprise\".\n \_\_\_\_\_If you need help,\
  \ take a look at the instructions for the Fortune Cookie recipe.\n  2. When the\
  \ user presses the button 5 times, show them a jack-in-the-box using the methods\
  \ below.\n     (A sample jackInTheBox.png file is provided in the default package)\n\
  \  private void showPicture(String fileName) { \n\_\_\_\_\_try {\n\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\
  \_\_\_\_JLabel imageLabel = createLabelImage(fileName);\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_JFrame\
  \ frame = new JFrame();\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_frame.setDefaultCloseOperation(JFrame.EXIT_ON_CLOSE);\n\
  \_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_frame.add(imageLabel);\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_frame.setVisible(true);\n\
  \_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_frame.pack();\n\_\_\_\_\_} catch (Exception e) {\n\_\_\_\_\_\
  \_\_\_\_\_e.printStackTrace();\n\_\_\_\_\_}\n}\n  private JLabel createLabelImage(String\
  \ fileName) {\n\t\_\_\_\_\_try {\t\t\t\n\t\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_URL imageURL = getClass().getResource(fileName);\n\
  \t\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_if (imageURL == null) {\n\t\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\
  System.err.println(\"Could not find image \" + fileName);\n\t\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\
  \_\_\_\_\_return new JLabel();\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_} else {\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\
  \_\_\_\_\_\_Icon icon = new ImageIcon(imageURL);\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\
  JLabel imageLabel = new JLabel(icon);\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_return imageLabel;\n\
  \   \_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_}  \n\_\_\_\_\_} catch (Exception e) {\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\
  \_\_System.err.println(\"Could not find image \" + fileName);\n\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\
